---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro'
import CallToAction from '../components/CallToAction.astro'
---

<MainLayout title="Video Content Strategy - Alpha Performance Lab" description="Comprehensive video content strategy for YouTube channel growth, including pillar review videos, educational content, and social media optimization.">

<article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
  <header class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
      Video Content Strategy & Production Plan
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
      Comprehensive video content strategy for YouTube channel growth, including pillar review videos, 
      educational content, and social media optimization.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    
    <!-- Video Content Overview -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Video Content Overview</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Content Strategy Goals</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Primary Objectives</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Build authority in brainwave entrainment niche</li>
              <li>• Drive traffic to affiliate website</li>
              <li>• Establish thought leadership</li>
              <li>• Create educational value</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Target Metrics</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• 10,000 subscribers in 6 months</li>
              <li>• 100,000 total views</li>
              <li>• 5% click-through rate to website</li>
              <li>• 50% watch time retention</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pillar Review Video Script -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Pillar Review Video Script (15 minutes)</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Video Structure</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Hook (0-30 seconds)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                "After 30 days of testing The Edison Wave, I discovered something that changed 
                my entire approach to focus and productivity. Here's what I found..."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-green-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Introduction (30-60 seconds)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Introduce yourself, your background in neuroscience, and what The Edison Wave is. 
                Set expectations for the review.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-purple-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <span class="text-purple-600 font-bold text-sm">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Science Explanation (1-3 minutes)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Explain alpha brainwaves, their benefits, and how brainwave entrainment works. 
                Use simple diagrams and animations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-orange-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold text-sm">4</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Testing Protocol (3-5 minutes)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Detail your 30-day testing methodology, including measurements taken, 
                tools used, and data collection methods.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-red-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <span class="text-red-600 font-bold text-sm">5</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Results & Analysis (5-10 minutes)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Present your findings with charts, graphs, and personal observations. 
                Include both quantitative and qualitative results.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-teal-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <span class="text-teal-600 font-bold text-sm">6</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Pros & Cons (10-12 minutes)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Honest assessment of the product's strengths and weaknesses. 
                Compare to alternatives and provide context.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-indigo-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold text-sm">7</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Bonus Package (12-14 minutes)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Showcase the $197 bonus package and explain how to access it. 
                Highlight the exclusive value proposition.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-pink-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <span class="text-pink-600 font-bold text-sm">8</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Final Verdict & CTA (14-15 minutes)</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Provide your final recommendation and clear call-to-action. 
                Include affiliate link and bonus information.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- YouTube Shorts Strategy -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">YouTube Shorts Strategy (60-second edits)</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Short #1: "Alpha Wave Benefits"</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Hook (0-5 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-green-700 text-sm">"Did you know alpha waves can boost your focus by 23%?"</p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Content (5-50 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-green-700 text-sm">Quick explanation of alpha waves and their benefits with visual aids.</p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">CTA (50-60 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-green-700 text-sm">"Link in bio to learn more about The Edison Wave!"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-4">Short #2: "30-Day Results"</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Hook (0-5 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">"I tested The Edison Wave for 30 days. Here's what happened..."</p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Content (5-50 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">Show key results with before/after graphics and personal testimony.</p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">CTA (50-60 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">"Full review link in bio!"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-4">Short #3: "Morning Routine"</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Hook (0-5 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-purple-700 text-sm">"My morning routine that changed everything..."</p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Content (5-50 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-purple-700 text-sm">Quick walkthrough of morning routine incorporating The Edison Wave.</p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">CTA (50-60 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-purple-700 text-sm">"Try it yourself - link in bio!"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-800 mb-4">Short #4: "Bonus Package"</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Hook (0-5 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm">"Get $197 in bonuses FREE with The Edison Wave!"</p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Content (5-50 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm">Quick showcase of bonus items and their value.</p>
            
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">CTA (50-60 seconds)</h4>
            <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm">"Claim yours now - link in bio!"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Production Requirements -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Production Requirements</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Equipment Needed</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• 4K camera or smartphone with good quality</li>
            <li>• External microphone (lapel or shotgun)</li>
            <li>• Ring light or softbox lighting</li>
            <li>• Tripod for stable shots</li>
            <li>• Green screen (optional)</li>
            <li>• Editing software (DaVinci Resolve, Premiere Pro)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Technical Specifications</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Resolution: 1080p minimum, 4K preferred</li>
            <li>• Frame rate: 30fps for main content, 60fps for shorts</li>
            <li>• Audio: 48kHz, 16-bit minimum</li>
            <li>• Aspect ratio: 16:9 for main videos, 9:16 for shorts</li>
            <li>• File format: MP4 (H.264 codec)</li>
            <li>• File size: Under 128GB for YouTube upload</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Calendar -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Content Calendar & Schedule</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Weekly Upload Schedule</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Monday</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Educational short (60 seconds)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Wednesday</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Tips & tricks short (60 seconds)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Friday</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Main video (10-15 minutes)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Sunday</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Community update short (60 seconds)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SEO & Optimization -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">SEO & Optimization Strategy</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Title Optimization</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Include primary keyword in first 60 characters</li>
            <li>• Use power words: "Review", "Tested", "Results"</li>
            <li>• Add numbers: "30-Day", "5 Ways", "2025"</li>
            <li>• Create curiosity: "What I Discovered"</li>
            <li>• Include brand name: "The Edison Wave"</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Description Optimization</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• First 125 characters are crucial</li>
            <li>• Include target keywords naturally</li>
            <li>• Add timestamps for longer videos</li>
            <li>• Include relevant hashtags</li>
            <li>• Add call-to-action</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="bg-green-600 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Ready to Start Your Video Content Strategy?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-green-100 mb-8">
        Get The Edison Wave today and start creating compelling video content. 
        Plus, receive $197 in exclusive bonuses FREE!
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <CallToAction 
          text="Get The Edison Wave + $197 Bonuses" 
          href="https://2be6ay18106x2x8dua0ezqwh-q.hop.clickbank.net/?&traffic_source=google&traffic_type=organic"
          variant="success"
          size="lg"
        />
        <CallToAction 
          text="Read Our Complete Review" 
          href="/review"
          variant="secondary"
          size="lg"
        />
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</article>

</MainLayout>
